		"Welcome to ArbeitszeitCheck": "Welcome to ArbeitszeitCheck",
		"This quick tour will help you get started with time tracking. You can skip this tour at any time.": "This quick tour will help you get started with time tracking. You can skip this tour at any time.",
		"ArbeitszeitCheck helps you track your working hours while ensuring compliance with German labor law (ArbZG) and GDPR requirements.": "ArbeitszeitCheck helps you track your working hours while ensuring compliance with German labor law (ArbZG) and GDPR requirements.",
		"Clock In and Out": "Clock In and Out",
		"Use the \"Clock In\" button to start tracking your work time. When you finish, click \"Clock Out\" to stop.": "Use the \"Clock In\" button to start tracking your work time. When you finish, click \"Clock Out\" to stop.",
		"The system automatically tracks your working hours and ensures compliance with legal requirements.": "The system automatically tracks your working hours and ensures compliance with legal requirements.",
		"Take Breaks": "Take Breaks",
		"After 6 hours of work, you need at least 30 minutes of break time. After 9 hours, you need 45 minutes.": "After 6 hours of work, you need at least 30 minutes of break time. After 9 hours, you need 45 minutes.",
		"Use \"Start Break\" and \"End Break\" to record your breaks. The system will remind you if you forget.": "Use \"Start Break\" and \"End Break\" to record your breaks. The system will remind you if you forget.",
		"Your Dashboard": "Your Dashboard",
		"The dashboard shows your daily, weekly, and monthly working hours, overtime balance, and vacation days remaining.": "The dashboard shows your daily, weekly, and monthly working hours, overtime balance, and vacation days remaining.",
		"You can also view your time entries in a calendar or timeline format.": "You can also view your time entries in a calendar or timeline format.",
		"Request Absences": "Request Absences",
		"You can request vacation days, sick leave, or other absences through the Absences section.": "You can request vacation days, sick leave, or other absences through the Absences section.",
		"Your manager will review and approve or reject your requests.": "Your manager will review and approve or reject your requests.",
		"Export Your Data": "Export Your Data",
		"Under GDPR, you have the right to access your personal data. You can export all your time tracking data at any time.": "Under GDPR, you have the right to access your personal data. You can export all your time tracking data at any time.",
		"Go to Settings to export your data in JSON format.": "Go to Settings to export your data in JSON format.",
		"You're All Set!": "You're All Set!",
		"You now know the basics of ArbeitszeitCheck. Start by clocking in to begin tracking your time!": "You now know the basics of ArbeitszeitCheck. Start by clocking in to begin tracking your time!",
